content: I don't have access to up-to-date pricing information for shuttle services, and prices can vary depending on many factors such as time of day, season, demand, and location. however, some popular and affordable shuttle services that operate in the area include super shuttle, disneyland resort express, and karmel shuttle. you can check out their websites to compare prices and find the cheapest option for your trip. it's always a good idea to book in advance to secure the best rates.
